m\": 1610, \"to\": 1619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So it's not like, you know, 'Meet me at the table at five o'clock.\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1689, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1672}, {\"ngram\": \"five o'clock\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We need to discuss work tomorrow.'\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1713}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That does not happen.\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1746, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But he's been around the game of basketball since he was born.\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1778}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Obviously, I have played in the NBA longer than he's been alive, so he understands the nuances of it, as far as just being around the game.\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1844, \"end\": 1847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999999999979536, \"rank\": 2.068373184263977e-12, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the nuances\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1906}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But now he's a man, and it's time for him to learn and get better with that.\\\"\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 2031, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1972}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 1987}]}, {\"sentence\": \"- Plenty 'in the tank' -James meanwhile said being part of the USA's gold medal-winning team in Paris, when he formed part of a